Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,1065)}古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,古 古蕾雅學姐
