Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,早…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 古蕾雅 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54\pos(1288,14)}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說來這裡是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,安 讓我把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,脫皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那個… 我長個子的時候偶爾會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的頭髮都長長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 難道說你的胸也變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可能…真變大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看來不要打擾你就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對 對不起 為我費了這麼多心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,別介意 別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來我也沒幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道你是在脫皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我就該一直陪著凌亂的古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你折騰的可厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,安 你拿著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算把它當作我們成長的證明留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}安這個小笨蛋
